                <p>Ahead of Halloween, Fanatical has kicked off a big sale with some scary good deals on horror hits as well as games with tropes from the genre such as zombies, vampires, and ghosts. <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jdoqocy.com%2Fclick-100770772-13797872%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanatical.com%2Fen%2Fgame%2Fmarvel-s-spider-man-remastered&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fhorror-game-sale-features-scary-good-deals-on-silent-hill-2-cult-of-the-lamb-and-more%2F1100-6527424%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Marvel's Spider-Man Remastered</a> and <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kqzyfj.com%2Fclick-100770772-13797872%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanatical.com%2Fen%2Fgame%2Fmarvel-s-spider-man-miles-morales&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fhorror-game-sale-features-scary-good-deals-on-silent-hill-2-cult-of-the-lamb-and-more%2F1100-6527424%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Miles Morales</a> are also prominently featured on the <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jdoqocy.com%2Fclick-100770772-13797872%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanatical.com%2Fen%2Fcollections%2Ffrightfest-promo-2024&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fhorror-game-sale-features-scary-good-deals-on-silent-hill-2-cult-of-the-lamb-and-more%2F1100-6527424%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Frightfest sale landing page</a>. Since Spider-Man is a very popular Halloween costume, we suppose it fits the theme--and both games are nearly 50% off, so they are awesome deals regardless. Most of the games in the sale are Steam keys that can be redeemed instantly.</p><p>The standalone discounts are complemented by the new <strong><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.anrdoezrs.net%2Fclick-100770772-13797872%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanatical.com%2Fen%2Fpick-and-mix%2Fbuild-your-own-frightmare-bundle&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fhorror-game-sale-features-scary-good-deals-on-silent-hill-2-cult-of-the-lamb-and-more%2F1100-6527424%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">build-your-own Frightmare Bundle</a></strong> with 19 games to choose from, including Doom (2016), The Evil Within 1 and 2, and Dead Island Definitive Collection, which actually comes with three games. Best of all, you could get all of the Steam games we just listed for only $11.68 total.</p><p>One of our favorite standalone deals is for the recently released <strong><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.anrdoezrs.net%2Fclick-100770772-13797872%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanatical.com%2Fen%2Fgame%2Fsilent-hill-2&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fhorror-game-sale-features-scary-good-deals-on-silent-hill-2-cult-of-the-lamb-and-more%2F1100-6527424%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Silent Hill 2</a></strong> remake, which is now just $54.59 (was $70). The remake features radically improved gameplay and modernized graphics with support for advanced tech like ray tracing, so it's a great match for high-end gaming rigs. It also benefits from a new over-the-shoulder perspective. This deal disappears after Halloween, however, so you donâ€™t have much time left to cash in on the offer. If you want a handful of digital goodies, check out <strong><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.anrdoezrs.net%2Fclick-100770772-13797872%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanatical.com%2Fen%2Fgame%2Fsilent-hill-2-digital-deluxe&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fhorror-game-sale-features-scary-good-deals-on-silent-hill-2-cult-of-the-lamb-and-more%2F1100-6527424%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Silent Hill 2's Digital Deluxe Edition</a></strong>, which comes with a digital art book and soundtrack, for $62.39 (was $80).</p><div tabindex="0" data-id="1174254361" data-promo-id="0" data-user-has-ads="1" data-video="{&quot;id&quot;:6465285,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Silent%20Hill%202%20PS2%20Vs%20Silent%20Hill%202%20Remake%20PS5%20Graphics%20Comparison&quot;,&quot;lengthSeconds&quot;:481,&quot;startTime&quot;:0,&quot;autoplay&quot;:false,&quot;share&quot;:{&quot;linkUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/silent-hill-2-ps2-vs-silent-hill-2-remake-ps5-graphics-comparison\/2300-6465285\/&quot;,&quot;embedUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/embed\/6465285\/&quot;,&quot;embedHtml&quot;:{&quot;640&quot;:&quot;\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<iframe src=\&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/embed\/6465285\/\&quot; height=\&quot;360\&quot; width=\&quot;640\&quot; scrolling=\&quot;no\&quot; frameborder=\&quot;\&quot; webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen><\/iframe>&quot;,&quot;480&quot;:&quot;\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<iframe src=\&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/embed\/6465285\/\&quot; height=\&quot;270\&quot; width=\&quot;480\&quot; scrolling=\&quot;no\&quot; frameborder=\&quot;\&quot; webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen><\/iframe>&quot;}},&quot;device&quot;:&quot;other&quot;,&quot;isDevice&quot;:false,&quot;isLiveStream&quot;:false,&quot;videoType&quot;:&quot;video-on-demand&quot;,&quot;countdownTime&quot;:0,&quot;guid&quot;:&quot;gs-2300-6465285&quot;,&quot;ageGateCookieName&quot;:&quot;videoAgeGateBirthday&quot;,&quot;watchedCookieName&quot;:&qu